            <who name="Christian Boulanger">info</who>
            <bug_when>2012-08-05 11:00:53 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>At the moment, &quot;runtime&quot; settings such as --no-progress-indicator cannot be specified in config.json, which means that in environments where such settings must be the default (e.g., in Clou9IDE, where the progress indicator messes up the output), the setting needs to be typed in every time, which is confusing for new users and unconvenient for everybody. There might me a use case for being able to specify such 
settings in config.json that affect the runtime behaviour of the generator and are meant to affect all jobs (CACHE being an obvious example).</thetext>
          </long_desc>
